edu.jhu.cs.pl.group18.CurseOfMalphamondModel.Actor

Class Actor

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.jhu.cs.pl.group18.CurseOfMalphamondModel.Actor.Actor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Boss, Character, Monster

    public abstract class Actor
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provide a super class interface for all the actors in the game. Here we enclose the common attributes for all kinds of the actors in the game.
